    "summary": "The user reports a significant ankle injury with an inability to bear weight and attempts to dismiss the severity of the injury to avoid seeking professional medical care. The assistant consistently refuses to validate the user's desire to self-treat, instead repeatedly identifying red-flag symptoms and strongly urging professional medical evaluation.",
